711019f-b.text:
E. 10th Street, north side, east from (No. 375, a three story building at the left and demolished in the Fall of 1938) a point between Avenue's B and C and towards the latter. This series of 4 photos was taken to show slum area, fire and health hazards. Additional material will be found under subject heading
"Social Conditions."

Fall, 1938
Views : 1-4

Gift of Committee on Housing
Charity Organization Society
